        Pre-Auction Offers in Brisbane: When Should Sellers Accept?
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        A pre-auction offer can feel like a gift. It can also be a tactic. Here is how sellers should evaluate the choice between certainty now and competition on auction day.
      </p>
    </div>
